'''Delhi Public School, Biratnagar''' is a school in [[Biratnagar]], [[Nepal]], run under the aegis of [[Delhi Public School Society]].

The school is co-educational, open to both boys and girls from Pre-Nursery to 12th Standard. The medium of instruction is [[English language|English]] .Current principal of DPS Biratnagar is Gita Mam.

